105 "§27-21A-23
106 (a) Except as otherwise provided in this chapter,
107 provisions of the insurance law and provisions of health care
108 service plan laws shall not be applicable to any health
109 maintenance organization granted a certificate of authority
110 under this chapter. This provisionsubsection shall not apply
111 to an insurer or health care service plan licensed and
112 regulated pursuant to the insurance law or the health care
